"      Patient information: Lung cancer (The Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?23/38/24162?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Small cell lung cancer (The Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
